# Environment variables — documented shape only (docs/10 §3, §7).
#
# Tier 0 needs NONE of these: the launch is a static site with no server
# and no secrets. This file exists so the shape is documented before the
# database sprint (docs/09) introduces the first real secrets. Copy to
# `.env.local` for local dev when those land. NEVER commit real values —
# production/preview secrets live in the host's env store (Render).

